title: Philosophical Mad Libs with Ari Shaffir & Joe DeRosa | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 83
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This week the babes are LIVE FROM JOEY ROSES!!! They are joined by comedians Ari Shaffir & Joe DeRosa. Chrissy goes full philosophy all over everyones asses. Would you want a person chef or driver?! Sal never has to pee. What height makes you a "lil person". How tall is Danny DeVito? Awkward stories from the bedroom. DeRosa has pulled out his back and is PAIN. Ari talks about filming his special "Jew". Chris is a flake. The worst tattoos. Sal talks about one of his classmates who said the craziest thing in front of the class. Joe wants him and Chris to get the tattoos they promised the fans. Ari's dog joins the program and does a crying trick. Who is playing the new Mr.Smith in the new Mr and Mrs Smith tv series. DeRosa goes OFF THE RAILS!
